I will do a series of Bible verses and reflections in smoothie bowls, and I plan to learn to do more food art than just flowers so I can challenge myself and inspire you all 🤗.I know that all of us inspire each other to be good and improve some skills, that's why I love to do it all the time.

Ingredients 

-1/2 a cup of canned chickpeas
-3 kiwis 
-2 strawberries 
-Sprinkle some pumpkin seeds 
-Sprinkle coconut flakes 
-Sprinkle some DIY granola or already made one.
-A dash of cinnamon 
-1/2 of frozen mangoes
-2 tablespoons of rolled oats 

 
Reflection 

Today I realized that I'm beyond blessed and have plenty of having  something that you cannot find,earn or buy in this world and that is Jesus's grace. In 1 timothy 1:1 says
"The grace of our Lord was poured out on me abundantly, along with the faith and love that are in Christ Jesus."

God's grace doesn't depend on my bank account ,how I feel,my friends,etc. God's grace depend solely and primary on Jesus sacrifice in the cross.

So if I have cancer like Chadwick Boseman, who was christian and now is in the presence of his beloved and faithful Lord Jesus  rejoicing in his presence eternally without pain, I rejoice!🙌.

If I have to wait 8 years to pursue the career that I love ,I rejoice ,if I'm a martyr in Afghanistan and they kill me ,I rejoice.If I don't have a job,I rejoice.Do you see,God grace doesn't depend on what we see or understand depends on the gospel.

